'''Brachinas''', also known as '''pleasure devils''', were insidious [[baatezu]],{{Cite dungeon/140/Heart of Hellfire Mountain|78}} particularly the servants of the [[god]]s.

In the infernal rankings of devils, brachinas were generally concluded to be of the same rank as [[cornugon]]s.

